genresAdvancedInfo.name: ostschlager
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Also originating from East Germany, Ostschlager is a genre of pop music that combines traditional German Schlager with elements of rock and pop. The lyrics often focus on love and relationships, and the music is known for its catchy melodies and upbeat rhythms.
